  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators are developing and then testing whether Mindfulness-Based Stress Reduction,
      a group-based instruction for increasing mindfulness, reduces anxiety and depressive symptoms
      and improves cognitive functioning in older adults.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
